{"id":79676,"title":"The Vicious Worm: a computer-based Taenia solium education tool.","abstract":"Ignorance is a major obstacle for the effective control of diseases. To provide evidence-based knowledge about prevention and control of Taenia solium cysticercosis, we have developed a computer-based education tool: 'The Vicious Worm'. The tool targets policy makers, professionals, and laypeople, and comprises educational materials including illustrated short stories, videos, and scientific texts designed for the different target groups. We suggest that evidence-based health education is included as a specific control measure in any control programme. ","date":"2014-07-28","categories":"Parasitic Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25017127","annotations":[{"name":"Education","weight":0.62135,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Education"},{"name":"Disease","weight":0.569488,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disease"},{"name":"Health","weight":0.521073,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health"},{"name":"Science","weight":0.360168,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Science"},{"name":"Knowledge","weight":0.173712,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Knowledge"},{"name":"Health education","weight":0.133827,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Health_education"},{"name":"Policy","weight":0.107046,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Policy"},{"name":"Preventive medicine","weight":0.107046,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Preventive_medicine"},{"name":"Cysticercosis","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cysticercosis"},{"name":"Taenia solium","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Taenia_solium"},{"name":"Tool","weight":0.0297435,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tool"},{"name":"Short story","weight":0.0287783,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia